label: brokenProduce
comment: The physically broken or cracked, impacting overall integrity of the product or item.

label: ddp
comment: Damaged & Discolored Pods (DDP) respresents the pods with visible damage, discoloration, or other aesthetic defects.

label: foreignMatter
comment: The presence of any unwanted materials, such as dirt, stones, or contaminants.

label: fineProduce
comment: The agricultural produce that meet the desired quality standards without significant defects.

label: mip
comment: Mold Infested Pods (MIP) represents the pods showing signs of mold growth, indicating spoilage or improper storage.

label: pows
comment: Pods without Stem (POWS) represents the harvested agricultural produce such as vegetables, fruits, etc. that lack stems, which may impact overall appearance and handling.

label: moistureLevel
comment: The amount moisture content in an item corresponding to this observation.
